#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.zipf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Zipf distribution."
msgstr "从 Zipf 分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a Zipf distribution with specified parameter `a` >"
" 1."
msgstr "样本从参数为 `a` > 1 的 Zipf 分布中抽取。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:6 of
msgid ""
"The Zipf distribution (also known as the zeta distribution) is a "
"continuous probability distribution that satisfies Zipf's law: the "
"frequency of an item is inversely proportional to its rank in a frequency"
" table."
msgstr ""
"Zipf 分布（也称为 zeta 分布）是一种满足 Zipf 定律的连续概率分布：一个项目"
"的频率与其在频率表中的排名成反比。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:11 of
msgid "Distribution parameter. Should be greater than 1."
msgstr "分布参数。应大于 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:13 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``a`` is a scalar. Otherwise, ``mt.array(a).size`` samples "
"are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``a`` 是标量，则返回单个值。否则抽取 "
"``mt.array(a).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:18 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:20 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:22 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:25 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Zipf distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的 Zipf 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.zipf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:31 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution, or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:34 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:35 of
msgid "The probability density for the Zipf distribution is"
msgstr "Zipf 分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:37 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{x^{-a}}{\\zeta(a)},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:39 of
msgid "where :math:`\\zeta` is the Riemann Zeta function."
msgstr "其中 :math:`\\zeta` 是黎曼 Zeta 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:41 of
msgid ""
"It is named for the American linguist George Kingsley Zipf, who noted "
"that the frequency of any word in a sample of a language is inversely "
"proportional to its rank in the frequency table."
msgstr ""
"该分布以美国语言学家 George Kingsley Zipf 命名，他指出在语言样本中任何"
"单词的频率与其在频率表中的排名成反比。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:46 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.zipf.zipf:47 of
msgid ""
"Zipf, G. K., \"Selected Studies of the Principle of Relative Frequency in"
" Language,\" Cambridge, MA: Harvard Univ. Press, 1932."
msgstr ""

